snippet.title: Sopa: Tale of the Stolen Potato - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Get another look at Sopa: Tale of the Stolen Potato in this trailer for the upcoming emotional narrative adventure game about the things we pass along. Sopa: Tale of the Stolen Potato will be available on Game Pass, Xbox, Windows, and Steam.
